e Pack #2</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://frosty.media">Frosty Media</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6:"Austin";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:5087:"<p class="alert">This plugin is an extension and requires <a href="https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/" title="Custom Login">Custom Login</a> (version <strong>3.x</strong>) which can be downloaded for free <a href="https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/">here</a>.</p><p>Have you wanted to add that extra touch to your WordPress login page? Have you been looking for ways to customize every part of your site to your personal or business brand? </p>\n<p>My guess is you&#8217;ve answered yes to one of those questions. With <a href="http://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/" title="Custom Login 3.0">Custom Login</a> it&#8217;s easy to brand your login page with the change of a few settings.</p>\n<h3>Adding Custom Style</h3>\n<p>What this style pack offers is four customized settings that you could activate at the click of a button. Upon activation you can do nothing and enjoy the new custom login style or tinker with the settings by adding your own logo or additional CSS, HTML or jQuery.</p>\n<h4>#1 The <em>Car Enthusiast</em> Style</h4>\n<p><img src="https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-wrx-sunset-1024x797.png" alt="Custom Login Car Enthusiast" width="1024" height="797" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-37576" /><br />\n<em>This style is for the car enthusiast, the background is a 2015 WRX on the beach. The form will slide down with CSS3 animation.</em></p>\n<h4>#2 The <em>Winter Wonderland</em> Style</h4>\n<p><img src="https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-login-snow-no-turn-1024x797.png" alt="Custom Login Snow" width="1024" height="797" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-37578" /><br />\n<em>This style pack has that fresh snow ovcast feeling. The form will slide in with CSS3 animation.</em></p>\n<h4>#3 The <em>Squirrel</em> Style</h4>\n<p><img src="https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-squirrel-tree-1024x768.png" alt="Custom Login Squirrel Tree" width="1024" height="768" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-37579" /><br />\n<em>This style pack is has fun written all over it, bright green with a squirrel looking right at you. The form will flip in with CSS3 animation.</em></p>\n<h4>#4 The <em>Dutch Vacation</em> Style</h4>\n<p><img src="https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-dutch-aruba-fade-up-1024x768.png" alt="Custom Login Dutch Aruba" width="1024" height="768" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-37580" /><br />\n<em>This style pack has that dark secretive vibe. The form will slide in with CSS3 animation.</em></p>\n<h3>How-to install</h3>\n<p>Follow this <a href="//frosty.media/docs/installing-custom-login-extensions/">documentation</a> guide.</p>\n<h3>Screenshots</h3>\n<a href=''https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-2/cl-style-wrx-sunset/''><img width="150" height="150" src="https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-wrx-sunset-150x150.png" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="Custom Login Car Enthusiast" /></a>\n<a href=''https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-2/cl-login-snow-no-turn/''><img width="150" height="150" src="https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-login-snow-no-turn-150x150.png" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="Custom Login Snow" /></a>\n<a href=''https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-2/cl-style-squirrel-tree/''><img width="150" height="150" src="https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-squirrel-tree-150x150.png" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="Custom Login Squirrel Tree" /></a>\n<a href=''https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-2/cl-style-dutch-aruba-fade-up/''><img width="150" height="150" src="https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-dutch-aruba-fade-up-150x150.png" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="Custom Login Dutch Aruba" /></a>\n<a href=''https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-2/cl-style-dutch-fade-up/''><img width="150" height="150" src="https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-dutch-fade-up-150x150.gif" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="cl-style-dutch-fade-up" /></a>\n<a href=''https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-2/cl-style-snow-fade-down/''><img width="150" height="150" src="https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-snow-fade-down-150x150.gif" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="cl-style-snow-fade-down" /></a>\n<a href=''https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-2/cl-style-squirrel-flip-in/''><img width="150" height="150" src="https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-squirrel-flip-in-150x150.gif" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="cl-style-squirrel-flip-in" /></a>\n<a href=''https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-2/cl-style-wrx-fade-down/''><img width="150" height="150" src="https://frosty.media/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/cl-style-wrx-fade-down-150x150.gif" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="cl-style-wrx-fade-down" /></a>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-2/">Style Pack #2</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://frosty.media">Frosty Media</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:60:"https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-2/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/r